OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777990267
OL,3,CPlymouth's latest bomb saga provides
OL,4,Canother history lesson
OL,6,FThe words of Colonel Nick Handy, a
OL,7,Fstraight-talking senior explosives
OL,8,Fofficer who oversaw the discovery and
OL,9,Fdetonation of a 250kg German Second
OL,10,FWorld War bomb in Plymouth.
OL,12,FAlong with his undoubted abilities as
OL,13,Fan ordnance technician, Col Handy has
OL,14,Fa refreshing ability to cut through
OL,15,Fthe corporate jargon we often hear
OL,16,Ffrom those in positions of power, and
OL,17,Fget straight to the point.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
