PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777990267
OL,3,CPlymouth's latest bomb saga provides
OL,4,Canother history lesson
OL,6,FSpeaking to the media following
OL,7,FFriday's successful end to the city's
OL,8,Flatest bomb saga, he looked back at
OL,9,Fhow and why so many of these devices
OL,10,Fended up in the city.
OL,12,F"Towards the end of the war, pilots
OL,13,Fused to drop bombs as they reached
OL,14,FBritain, because all they wanted to do
OL,15,Fwas get home to Germany,' Col Handy
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"The south coast is probably littered
OL,19,Fwith bombs. Have we found them all?
OL,20,FAbsolutely not. Will we find more?
OL,21,FAbsolutely.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777990267
OL,3,CPlymouth's latest bomb saga provides
OL,4,Canother history lesson
OL,6,F"But the military train well and hard
OL,7,Ffor this."
OL,9,FThis was the third German Second World
OL,10,FWar bomb to be uncovered in Plymouth
OL,11,Fin the past two years.
OL,13,FIt feels inevitable that as the city
OL,14,Fcontinues to develop, as more spades
OL,15,Fenter the ground to allow homes to be
OL,16,Fbuilt, we will continue to feel the
OL,17,Fimpact of history.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777990267
OL,3,CPlymouth's latest bomb saga provides
OL,4,Canother history lesson
OL,6,FThe explosion itself was genuinely
OL,7,Fshocking - a very loud bang, car
OL,8,Falarms squealing, and thick black
OL,9,Fsmoke filling the air.
OL,11,FBut once the dust had literally
OL,12,Fsettled, it became clear the operation
OL,13,Fwas a success. No damage has been
OL,14,Freported, residents are returning home
OL,15,Fand life can begin to return to normal.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
