OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777990267
OL,3,CPlymouth's latest bomb saga provides
OL,4,Canother history lesson
OL,6,FWhat has been striking over the past
OL,7,Fthree days is the sense of calm around
OL,8,FSouthway, not just from police,
OL,9,Fmilitary and council officials, but
OL,10,Ffrom those who had to leave their
OL,11,Fhomes and cope with all the disruption.
OL,13,FSome people have been understandably
OL,14,Fanxious and upset, but unearthing
OL,15,Fbombs is becoming a regular part of
OL,16,Flife in Plymouth.
OL,18,FEach time it happens, we get a
OL,19,Ffascinating, shocking, explosive
OL,20,Freminder of a dark time in the city's
OL,21,Fhistory.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
